# Zawiyah Quran App Assets

This folder contains religious content for the app:

## Folder Structure:
- `99namesofAllah/` - 99 Names of Allah 
- `flags/` - Country flags 
- `images/` - General images 
- `manzil/` - Manzil verses 
- `mushaf/` - Quran pages/images
- `duas.json` - Dua database (included here)

## Download Full Assets:
Due to large file size , full assets are hosted on Google Drive:

### Option 1: Download ZIP (Recommended)
[Download assets.zip](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1spYvRZb5NubmksRr6ERw5HqZ3loS-Msz/view?usp=sharing)

Extract to project root to restore full `assets/` folder.


## Setup Instructions:
1. Download assets.zip from above link
2. Extract to project root (overwrites this folder)
3. Run `flutter pub get`
4. The app should now have all assets
